The '''Citizens' Group on Electoral Process''' (CGEP) is a [[Pakistan]]i organisation created to ensure that [[free election|free]], fair and credible [[election]]s take place in the country. The first Chairman of the CGEP was Chief Justice (R) [[Saeeduzzaman Siddiqui]]<ref>[http://www.pildat.org/CGEP/ Citizens' Group on Electoral Process]</ref>

